  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 00c9c9bb92b3b44fb84ca335c48467d8, type: 3}
  m_Name: Dialogue_Act4_WendSource
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::Hollowfen.Dialogue.DialogueData
  _id: act4.wend.source
  _lines:
  - speaker: Wren
    text: The path climbed past the last of the Wendlight, and then the trees simply
      stopped. Rows of stumps. Drag-trails cut to mud. A camp gone cold, and the
      spring where a river should have started had run down to a trickle.
    isCloseup: 1
    voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: c7cc2113ca5794a9ba65643cc0c80c51, type: 3}
  - speaker: Wren
    text: This is where the river was broken.
    isCloseup: 1
    voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 2685869a6355d40549ee2a1494bff1b9, type: 3}
  - speaker: Hollin
    text: Not broken. Loosed.
    isCloseup: 1
    voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: c8e033a504a4749ed96ab064f5e9cc67, type: 3}
  - speaker: Wren
    text: That is worse.
    isCloseup: 0
    voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 8d66bf12f19784120a1f404222074d59, type: 3}
  - speaker: Hollin
    text: Yes.
    isCloseup: 1
    voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 70a2ed7a29ae848ceb3a9e23687792b3, type: 3}
  - speaker: Wren
    text: Aldermark at the edge. Of course something useful grows where harm stops.
    isCloseup: 1
    voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 43169af49ec7949e2b86be41a1591c26, type: 3}
  - speaker: Wren
    text: "The same mark was burned into stump after stump \u2014 the mark from the
      letter's seal."
    isCloseup: 1
    voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 1caaa748923264317bf34eca33d06134, type: 3}
  - speaker: Wren
    text: I did not cut them at first. I stood with my hands loose and let the anger
      become useful before I trusted myself with the knife.
    isCloseup: 1
    voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 7ea8433062cb444dc959b2c9c888d5b6, type: 3}
  - speaker: Wren
    text: Then I took a frond of the Aldermark, and I took the truth with it.
    isCloseup: 1
    voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 64006818cf6b14c74aaf95e5061932f5, type: 3}
